additional_house_rules: No smoking and no loud parties allowed. Pets are welcome, however a security deposit ($300) will be required and extra cleaning fees may apply, depending on condition at checkout. If you're booking a reservation for same day arrival, please send a message first as we may need some time to prepare. If you're booking a short reservation (1-2 nights), please message me first as well. Lastly, please respect neighbors... and enjoy New York to the fullest!
description:
Location is right in the center of Manhattan's Hells Kitchen, 2 blocks from Times Square. Close to all major metro lines so it's easy to get around the city using public transit. Remodeled apartment with eat-in kitchen. Everything you need to make yourself at home during your visit. I'd love to host you during your stay!
Important! If you have a last minute (same day) reservation, please inquire first (use red "contact host" button in "your host" section directly after reviews). Thank you.

Spacious 2 bedroom apartment steps from everything!
Please note, it is on the 4th floor and there is no elevator. We can definitely help with luggage and will meet you in person at the time of check in.

We will be available 24/7 by phone. Should a problem arise or you need extra towels or other things mid-stay, we are 10 minutes away.

The park across the street, all the cool restaurants and other major attractions are a short walk away.

Subway (C,E,A lines) is 2 blocks away. Other major lines (1,2,3,Q,N,R,W) are 3 blocks away.

When staying in the apartment as our guest- you are our friend and personal guest. Always remember that when you visit (if anyone asks) ;-)
